      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="528a49bb-a018-489a-ba1a-869159838edb" type="Noun">
          <Vi>con rùa</Vi>
          <En>A reptile with a hard shell that protects its body, typically moving slowly on land or in water.</En>
          <Example>The turtle slowly crossed the road to reach the pond on the other side.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="5cbef147-ddac-4263-90ec-3d18e1901a00">
              <Vi>Mô tả một con rùa đang bò trên cát hoặc bơi trong nước.</Vi>
              <En>Describing a turtle moving on sand or swimming in water.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="331c14e8-3269-4d07-aabc-2662e8089903">
              <Vi>Trong ngữ cảnh bảo tồn, nói về loài rùa biển đang bị đe dọa tuyệt chủng.</Vi>
              <En>In conservation contexts, referring to endangered sea turtle species.</En>
            </Situation>
